subject: Re: Attn Dear Beneficiary;
body:
Hello there,

I hope this message finds you well. I'm delighted to hear about the funds payment valued in Million USD credited in an ATM Master card by Eco Bank. That's quite a surprise!

Could you please provide me with more details about this? How did this come about? And why was I chosen for this?

Also, could you explain how the daily programmed fund payment works? It sounds interesting but I would like to understand it better.

I look forward to hearing from you soon.

Best regards.

Best wishes,
Ebony
